{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/14841", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/14841/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/14841/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/14841/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/14841", "id": 35562575, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzNTU2MjU3NQ==", "number": 14841, "title": "#[plugin_registrar] is not type-checked", "user": {"login": "kimhyunkang", "id": 10231, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEwMjMx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10231?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang", "html_url": "https://github.com/kimhyunkang", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kimhyunkang/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 100522, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMDA1MjI=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/I-crash", "name": "I-crash", "color": "e10c02", "default": false, "description": "Issue: The compiler crashes (SIGSEGV, SIGABRT, etc). Use I-ICE instead when the compiler panics."}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 6, "created_at": "2014-06-12T09:18:21Z", "updated_at": "2018-09-24T17:03:34Z", "closed_at": "2018-09-24T17:03:33Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "`#[plugin_registrar]` functions are not type-checked, which exposes unsafe memory content to the plugin modules. Nor are they checked for being `pub`.\r\n\r\nI could reproduce this on the latest nightly build for x64 linux. Minimal reproducing example follows.\r\n\r\nplugin_lib.rs :\r\n\r\n``` rust\r\n#![crate_id = \"plugin_lib\"]\r\n#![crate_type = \"dylib\"]\r\n\r\n#![feature(plugin_registrar)]\r\n\r\n#[plugin_registrar]\r\npub fn plugin_registrar(f: || -> ()) {\r\n    f()\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nplugin_test.rs : \r\n\r\n``` rust\r\n#![feature(phase)]\r\n\r\n#[phase(plugin)]\r\nextern crate plugin_lib;\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    ()\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\ncompilation:\r\n\r\n``` sh\r\nkimhyunkang@kanie:~/project/segfault_test$ rustc --version\r\nrustc 0.11.0-pre-nightly (4fdc27e 2014-06-10 23:37:06 -0700)\r\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\nkimhyunkang@kanie:~/project/segfault_test$ rustc plugin_lib.rs\r\nkimhyunkang@kanie:~/project/segfault_test$ rustc plugin_test.rs -L .\r\nSegmentation fault (core dumped)\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "steveklabnik", "id": 27786, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI3Nzg2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/27786?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik", "html_url": "https://github.com/steveklabnik", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https: